locations.description:
**Location:** Obtained by completing [Sellen's Quest](https://mapgenie.io/elden-ring/maps/the-lands-between?locationIds=164621):
- If you [challenged](https://mapgenie.io/elden-ring/maps/the-lands-between?locationIds=170413) her, she drops it;
- If you [assisted](https://mapgenie.io/elden-ring/maps/the-lands-between?locationIds=170412) her, it will drop on the ground in front of her, once you reload the area.

**Location:** Patrolling the area.

**Loot:**
- [Devonia's Hammer
](https://mapgenie.io/elden-ring/maps/the-shadow-realm?locationIds=382031)
- [Crucible Hammer-Helm
](https://mapgenie.io/elden-ring/maps/the-shadow-realm?locationIds=382032)
